data.description: This unique home in the New Deal School District features a wonderful heated 32'x14'indoor pool for year round swimming for fun and fitness.  Pool access from living room, master bedroom and backyard. The home has three bedrooms, three bathrooms, a spacious open concept living, dining, kitchen. Kitchen features granite counter tops, island, and butler's pantry! Lots of updates throughout.    Outdoors, behind the home, you will find a pergola and brick fireplace, great for entertaining and a view to the east of your 3.13 acre lot. Home has a 2 car west facing garage and double carport. There is another garage door/workshop on the south exterior of the home. There is also a storage shed adjacent to the outdoor kitchen.
